headline: YouTube Raises Price on TV Streaming Service to $82.99
summary: Get ready to pay more for YouTube TV.  YouTube said it would raise the monthly cost of its TV streaming service to $82.99, up from $72.99 starting Jan. 13.  “We don’t make these decisions lightly, and we realize this has an impact on our members,” YouTube said in an email to subscribers.
